   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rochiele, n brae subiri, dar ncordate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Strng viinul, i crac cu crac-l cuceresc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Cireele, alturi, sub frunze-mperecheate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T13"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">Roesc i se iubesc.</text:span></text:p>
