   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ascult: e grdina ntreag, ce unete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Simirea ei suav cu cntecul din noi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">i cerul din adncu-i de aur ne privete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T13"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">Zmbindu-ne prin foi.</text:span></text:p>
