   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Purtam n grai argintul curatelor izvoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">n cuget, visuri roze...  De via m-ncntam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">De soare m-mbtam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eram argint i soare... </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T13"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">Cnd aripi al meu suflet avea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Era ca o-nflorire de zile minunate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">De crini i roze roze...  Zmbeam copilros,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Voios i generos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Strin de rutate...</text:span></text:p>
