   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Numai aurul, el singur, mi lipsete-n ast lume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Numai el, dar fr dnsul sunt un biet neputincios...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Care suflet de-al meu suflet, care nume de-al meu nume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">S-ar lipi s ia povara unui trai srccios?</text:span></text:p>
