   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pe-oricare strzi cntau izvoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">i srutat de flori ce-mbat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tria oraul de-altdat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sub plopi de-argint, muiai n soare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Prostimea chiar era bogat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Prin curi aveau, mai toi, cuptoare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">n beciuri se eseau covoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">-o via-n veci mbelugat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tria oraul de-altdat.</text:span></text:p>
