   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sprgnd fluidicul su smalt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ca o sgeat de-aur treci. </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">n cer s-ajunge dintr-un salt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sau nu s-ajunge-n veci de veci.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I se mai d-n sfrit asalt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sub jar de patimi cnd te pleci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">n al tu suflet cnd n-ai alt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dect fiorii dulci i reci... </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">n cer s-ajunge dintr-un salt.</text:span></text:p>
