   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Rondelul rozelor din Cimegi</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">De flcri, de aur, pembe, argintate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nebun orgie de roze oriunde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">De boli agate, pe ziduri urcate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">i printre frunziuri de pomi ce le-ascunde.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pe ritmuri persane n strofe-aezate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Melodic, coloarea, coloarei rspunde... </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">De flcri, de aur, pembe, argintate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nebun orgie de roze oriunde.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Un neam a fost magul grdinii uitate.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rpit fu de visul cu tainice unde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">i dndu-le via ce-n suflet ptrunde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lsatu-le-a-n urm, n roze-nchegate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">De flcri, de aur, pembe, argintate.</text:span></text:p>
