   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Rondelul cascadelor de roze </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Urcnd pe pomi, zmbind pe cas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Se surp rozele grmad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sau ntocmesc cte-o cascad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pe vreo alee mai retras.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Parfumul lor purtat n strad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">ntinde-a lui subire plas...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Urcnd pe pomi, zmbind pe cas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Se surp rozele grmad.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">De-oricte stavili nu le pas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sunt un torent, sunt o cascad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ce-n voia soarelui se las,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dar ce, de cum sfresc s cad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Reurc-n pomi, zmbesc pe cas.</text:span></text:p>
