   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">O vraj i alb -albastr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Din ceruri, spre lume s-avnt. </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">A nopii sublim miastr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">E-ascuns-ntre roze, i cnt.</text:span></text:p>
