   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mai sunt nc roze  mai sunt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">i tot parfumate i ele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Aa cum au fost i acele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Cnd ceru-l credeam pe pmnt.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pe-atunci eram falnic avnt...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Priveam, dintre oameni, spre stele; </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mai sunt nc roze  mai sunt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">i tot parfumate i ele.</text:span></text:p>
